Create two `productFlavors` {noAnalytics|googlePlay}

The noAnalytics flavor will not send analytics as the `AnalyticsHelper` has been stubbed.  The implementation for analytics only
exists in the `googlePlay`.  Also only import the analytics library and declare analytic keys in `googlePlay` productFlavor
